      "comment": "BINNAWAY WARRIOR (3) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when fourth (30.34) in a OPEN at Mt Gambier. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Key runner on his best form. ELDRITCH (5) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by a neck (30.36) at this track. Looks a primary danger. FANTASTIC HELGA (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (31.18) at this track behind ELDRITCH in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Bold showing expected. PAW EVA (7) will give backers a sight.",
